        "score": 3,
        "is_accepted": true,
        "last_activity_date": 1394231127,
        "creation_date": 1394231127,
        "body": "<p>You can use <a href=\"http://docs.oracle.com/javase/6/docs/api/java/util/regex/Matcher.html#group%28int%29\" rel=\"nofollow\"><code>Matcher.group (int groupNum)<\/code><\/a>:<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>m.group ( AMReg.LocLink.getPlace() );\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Where <code>AMReg.LocLink.getPlace()<\/code> returns a group # 1, 2 etc.<\/p>\n",
